1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Stem cells can transform into any cell type — but they're not magic.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:10,400
Pluripotent stem cells have endless potential, while adult stem cells are more limited.

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:13,600
Approved uses include blood and bone marrow regeneration.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:16,000
But many applications are still experimental.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,600
The NIH emphasizes caution.

6
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:21,200
Unproven clinics may promise miracles, but often deliver disappointment.

7
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:25,600
Understanding stem cells means recognizing their power, but also their limits.

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,400
They’re tools for healing, not silver bullets.

9
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,000
Curious about stem cells?

